D.106.100 - The system shall support the ability to open, close, read only, reopen and respond to queries based on user rights.
D.106.200 - The system shall support the ability to filter issues based on records, fields, events and users.
D.106.300 - The system shall support the ability to upload files to queries. 
D.106.400 - The system shall support the ability to email and send messages via REDCap messenger with a link to issues.
D.106.500 - The system shall have the ability to verify and de-verify data value based on user rights.
D.106.600 - The system shall have the ability to automatically de-verify data that has been verified and subsequently changed.
D.106.700 - The system shall have the ability to add comments to fields.
D.106.800 - The system shall have the ability to filter  comments based on records, events, fields, users and keywords.